# SPEC_QIINT2_ALIGNED v2.0 — QIINT Measurement Framework for Kernel Runtime

## §0. INTENT & SCOPE

**QIINT2** = measurement framework cho QIINT physics foundation, operationalized cho kernel runtime (SURVIVAL + BRIDGE + CELL lifecycle).

**Ly do v2.0 rewrite:** v1.0 su dung paradigm `Π_body` tu tao, khong canonical theo `QIINT-DINH-NGHIA-CHINH-THUC.md`. v2.0 align voi vocabulary chinh thuc: **QIINT = gravitational field, QNEU = gravitational mass** (per SPEC_NEN v1.1 + session 20260413 definition).

**Scope:**
- Dinh nghia 8 calibration params cua kernel layer
- Cach DO tung param tu data that (KHONG guess)
- API contract cho qiint2.engine.ts (impl sau)
- Butterfly effect defense connection

**Out of scope:**
- QNEU persona scoring (thuoc SPEC_QNEU rieng)
- SiraSign signing (thuoc SPEC_SiraSIGN)

