## §2. BUTTERFLY EFFECT DEFENSE (2 vế hợp nhất)

### §2.1 Ve 1 — Chaos amplification (why we defend)

Per chaos theory + SPEC_RADIATION_UNIVERSAL §5:

```
Stress_total(n, t) = ∫₀ᵗ [Stress_X(τ) + R_time(τ)] dτ
```

Small input × infinite time → catastrophic cascade. 1 request nho co the amplify thanh DoS neu khong catch som.

### §2.2 Ve 2 — Measurement framework (how we defend)

Defense **CHI** work khi threshold la **MEASURED tu data that**, KHONG assumed.

```
K1_survival.decide(load) = measure(current_state)
                           compare(threshold_MEASURED_from_stress_test)
                           return ACCEPT | BACKPRESSURE | LOAD_SHED | CIRCUIT_BREAK
```

**Ket hop ve 1 + ve 2:**
> Chaos catches ONLY if calibration numbers are real.
> Guessed thresholds = false confidence = still vulnerable.

